These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, country, r&b, soul
1. the fan of ambient is on the left of the fan of soul##1
2. the fan of country is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
3. the fan of ambient is on the right of the fan of country##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | r&b | country | ambient | soul |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-2::.
4 different pets are kept: bird, guinea-pig, mouse, turtle
1. the owner of the turtle is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the bird is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Pet   | bird | mouse | guinea-pig | turtle |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, board-games, puzzles, rock-climbing
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby   | puzzles | baking | board-games | rock-climbing |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski, roller, van
1. the person driving the roller is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the van is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |  2   |    3    |  4  |
| Transport   | roller | bike | jet-ski | van |

 #################################
 
